documentsJson.title: Association for Education by Radio-Television, Membership, 1955-1956
documentsJson.description: 1955 to 1956 correspondence regarding the Association for Education by Radio-Television, including a membership pamphlet, potential member lists, overdue membership notices, and broadcasting newsletters from other organizations. Organization newsletters include Better Broadcasts, the National Society for the Study of Communication, and News and Views (World-Wide Sacred Hearts Program).
